# Task queue

When `TASKS.md` is in context for a batch run:

- Treat unchecked `- [ ]` lines under **Queue** as the work queue.
- Process one item at a time; mark `- [x]` in the file after verification.
- Do not mark items done in chat only — persist progress in `TASKS.md`.
